Github : https://github.com/zed-industries/zed

Zed is a code editor, written in Rust.
It has a growing community.

Pros[+]:
-Written in rustlang, it makes it light and fast. It's an advantage compared to Vscode(Industry standart), written in ElectronJS.
-Good and minimalistic design

Cons[-]:
-No code completion, yet
-No rainbow brackets and parantheses, yet
-Poor language server in a lot of languages and no code runner, yet
-Not very customizable
-Poor extension support
